text: Cathy Lund (born 23 March 1959) is a Canadian rower. She competed in the women's eight event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Canada Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from London, Ontario Category:Commonwealth Games medallists in rowing Category:Commonwealth Games bronze medallists for Canada Category:Rowers at the 1986 Commonwealth Games
